        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister when it is expected that a statement can be made as to the Government's plan for military and industrial demobilisation; and if it is proposed to issue a White Paper on the subject.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
